rt:model.rt:sub: Function printValue(ByVal p As Double) As String If (p < 0) Then printValue = Left(CStr(Round(p, 3)), 6) Else printValue = Left(CStr(Round(p, 3)), 5) End If End Function

Sub jef10_sb_cl_recalc()
'calc mean tmp_dbl_1 = 0 For tmp_int_1 = 0 To 5 tmp_dbl_1 = tmp_dbl_1 + jef10_sb_cl(tmp_int_1).Value next tmp_int_1 tmp_dbl_1 = tmp_dbl_1 / 6 'write mean jef10_sb_cl_mean = tmp_dbl_1
'calc deviations For tmp_int_1 = 0 To 5 jef10_sb_cl_dvt(tmp_int_1) = jef10_sb_cl(tmp_int_1).Value - tmp_dbl_1 next tmp_int_1 End Sub

Sub jef10_ne_cl_recalc()
'calc mean tmp_dbl_1 = 0 For tmp_int_1 = 0 To 2 tmp_dbl_1 = tmp_dbl_1 + jef10_ne_cl(tmp_int_1).Value next tmp_int_1 tmp_dbl_1 = tmp_dbl_1 / 3 'write mean jef10_ne_cl_mean = tmp_dbl_1
'calc deviations For tmp_int_1 = 0 To 2 jef10_ne_cl_dvt(tmp_int_1) = jef10_ne_cl(tmp_int_1).Value - tmp_dbl_1 next tmp_int_1
'calc 0.19 deviation jef_ne_cl_dvt_19(0) = jef_ne_cl_19(0).Value - tmp_dbl_1
'calc 0.18 deviation jef_ne_cl_dvt_18(0) = jef_ne_cl_18(0).Value - tmp_dbl_1 End Sub
